title: A Song With No Name
lyrics:
Do I love you too much?
Do I hold you too tight?
Have you had enough?
Shake me off in the night
If I had a gun

If I had a knife

If I had your love

If I was your wife



If I go on my own

And I see you in my dreams

And I hope to again

I have silently schemed



If I had a gun

If I had a knife

If I was the one

If I was your wife
